    description: "Melbourne is famous for its unpredictable weather — 'four seasons in one day' is a genuine local experience. The city sits in a temperature convergence zone where cold Antarctic fronts collide with hot northern air masses. The Southern Ocean and Port Phillip Bay create coastal microclimates.",
